Ali moves outside the off stump and lifts the length delivery over covers for a run. He wanted two initially but was sent back.
Very full, outside off. Azam swats it away towards the mid-wicket fence but Alzarri Joseph cuts it out and keeps it to just a couple.
Starts off with a bouncer, angled in at the body. Hasan Ali moves away from it.

OUT! TAKEN! Joshua Da Silva has been brilliant with his catching throughout the series. Holder bowls a slower one on middle. Ali makes room looking to slog it over the mid-wicket fence but manages to top edge it behind the keeper's head. Joshua Da Silva runs back and puts in the dive to take a magnificent catch.  Jason Holder gets rid of the dangerous Hasan Ali.
Howout: c Joshua Da Silva b Jason Holder

Commentary: Back of a length, on middle and leg. Babar Azam rocks back and works it towards deep square leg for a single.
A touch short and wide, cut away to deep point for one. Faheem Ashraf is off the mark.
Full and on the pads. Azam flicks it to deep mid-wicket for one. The lead is now 300 runs.
FOUR! Shorter one, on leg stump. Ashraf stays back and pulls it behind square on the leg side. Kieran Powell puts in the dive at the backward square leg fence but doesn't manage to stop the boundary.
Full and wide. Azam looks to squeeze it out but doesn't get any bat on it.
Length ball, outside off. Azam swats it through cover-point for a run.
Full and on middle. Ashraf drives it down to long on for one.
Mayers keeps up with his plan to bowl full and wide. Azam hits it straight to cover.
Full and wide again from Mayers. Azam manages to drive it past cover for a single.
Fuller delivery, on off stump. Ashraf swings it away to wide long on and collects a run.
Full and wide outside off. Ashraf slashes it down to third man for a run.
Slower delivery, pitched up on middle. Azam makes room and hits it to the cover region.
Full, on leg stump. Babar Azam digs it out to deep mid-wicket for one.
Fuller one, on middle and flicked away to wide long on for a run by Ashraf.
Slower and shorter, on leg stump. Azam pulls it to deep square leg and rotates the strike.

OUT! LBW! Jason Holder gets a near yorker in and reaps the reward. This one is angled in, very full on middle and Faheem Ashraf plays all around it. Ashraf looks to heave it on the leg side but gets trapped plumb in front. Holder appeals and the umpire has an easy decision to make. Jason Holder once again provides the breakthrough for his team.
Howout: lbw b Jason Holder

Commentary: Length ball, outside off. Azam lifts it over covers for a run.
Fullish delivery, outside off. Rizwan gets it through covers for a single.
Full and wide, Azam watchfully leaves it.
CLOSE! Length ball, outside off but it's bowled slower. Babar Azam looks to swing it on the leg side but gets the bottom edge which falls just short of Joshua Da Silva behind the stumps.
Full, outside off. Azam bunts it on the off side and takes a quick single.
Pitched up, around off. Rizwan drives it towards wide long off for a run.
A full-length ball, down the leg side. Rizwan looks to flick it away but misses. Joshua Da Silva dives to his left to make a sharp stop.

FOUR! EDGY! Only if there was a slip or two in place, there could have been a chance. A length ball, on off. Rizwan looks to push it out but gets an outside edge. The ball flies past Joshua Da Silva and races away to the boundary. Nothing the bowler can do about it.
Full and on off. Rizwan tucks it through mid-wicket for a single.
Back of a length and on off. Azam hangs back and pulls it through mid-wicket for another single.
BEATEN! A good-length ball, outside off. Rizwan moves across and looks to work it on the leg side but misses. The ball zips past the outside edge.
Good running! A length ball, on off. Rizwan pushes it through cover-point and gets a couple.
WIDE! Full and way outside the tramline. Azam leaves it alone. Wide called. Another extra run to the lead.
Full and sliding down leg. Azam looks to flick it away but misses. Joshua Da Silva collects the ball comfortably.
A length ball, way outside off. Azam watches it sail past him to the keeper. He wanted a wide but does not get one.
A length ball, on off. Azam pulls it away towards long on off the bottom end. They take one.
Holder takes away the pace from this one. A slower full length delivery, on off. Rizwan comes back and defends it back to the bowler.
Full and on middle. Rizwan flicks it through square leg for a single.

IN THE AIR..SAFE! A touch short, on off. Azam stays back and looks to play it across the line. He does so but from the toe end of the blade. The ball lands short off the fielder at long on. They take one.
A length ball, going down leg. Azam looks to pull it away but misses. Joshua Da Silva dives to his left but could not grab the ball easily.

OUT! CAUGHT! Alzarri Joseph grabs his second wicket of the innings. A length ball, on off. Babar Azam lifts it towards long on. Nkrumah Bonner comes running and takes a brilliant low catch. Pakistan have decided to declare on 176 for 6.
Howout: c Nkrumah Bonner b Alzarri Joseph

Commentary: Starts with a lovely outswinger. Bowls it on a length outside off and it shapes away. Kraigg Brathwaite leaves it alone.
Back of a length, on off. Brathwaite defends it off the back foot.
Fuller ball, on middle. Brathwaite tucks it past short leg and gets off the mark with a couple.
Length, on middle. Brathwaite works it through mid-wicket for a run.
A touch short and wide. Kieran Powell is off the mark with a single towards cover.
Pitched up, around off and well left by Kraigg Brathwaite.
Right on the money from the start. Length ball, on off and nipping in. Powell gets caught on the crease as the ball hits him high on the pads.
Fullish ball, outside off and left alone by Powell.
Length, around off. Powell shoulders arms to it.
Pitched up, on off. Powell drives it to mid off.
Length ball, outside off and left alone once again by Powell.
Fuller delivery, outside off. Powell goes for the cover drive but gets beaten.
Pitched up, on off. Brathwaite defends it off the front foot.
Back of a length, on the hips. Brathwaite turns it to fine leg for a single.
Short, but not short enough to pull. Powell looks to pull a length ball on leg stump but ends up getting a top edge over the slip cordon. They take two.
FOUR! Short of a length and this time Powell latches onto it. Powell pulls it through square leg and into the fence.
A touch fuller, on off. Powell drives it to cover-point.
Back of a length, angling down leg. Powell leaves it alone.
Length ball, swinging down leg. Kraigg Brathwaite doesn't play at it.
Full and on middle. Brathwaite digs it out.
On a good length, around off. Kraigg Brathwaite makes a good leave.

Fuller delivery, swinging down the leg side. Brathwaite looks to flick but misses and the ball clips the pads as it goes through to the keeper. Shaheen Afridi seems confident that there was bat on it but the umpire remains unmoved and Babar Azam doesn't take the review.
Full, on off. Kraigg Brathwaite presents the full face of the bat as he drives it past mid off for a couple.
Full again and on middle. Brathwaite clips it to deep square leg for one.
Pitched up, outside off and this one keeps low. Brathwaite looks to block it out but the ball sneaks under his willow.
Back of a length, around off. Brathwaite goes on the back foot and works it through mid-wicket for a run.
On a good length, around middle. Powell defends it to mid on.
Length ball, on off. Powell puts out a stride to block it.
Angled in full, on middle. Powell defends it back to the bowler.

NOT OUT! Pitched up fuller, around off and nipping back in sharply. Kieran Powell looks to defend but misses and the ball hits him on the pads. There is a huge appeal from the visitors but the umpire doesn't give it out. The angle was such that it might have been doing a bit too much and Babar Azam decides not to review.
A sharp bouncer, outside off. Kraigg Brathwaite leaves it alone for the keeper.
Fuller and outside off. Kraigg Brathwaite drives it to mid off, The fielder there makes a half stop.
A length ball, on off. Kraigg Brathwaite tucks it to the right of mid on.
Full and wide outside off. The ball moves away from the right-hander. Kraigg Brathwaite is not tempted by the width at all and he leaves it alone.
Afridi fires in a length ball, outside off. Brathwaite lets it go to the keeper.
A maiden for Shaheen Afridi. Good length and outside off. Brathwaite has no stroke to offer yet again.
On a length and outside off. Powell prods and shoulders his arms.
Abbas serves it on a length and outside off. Powell is happy to leave that one.
Good length and outside off. Left alone by Powell.
A length ball, angled into the pads. Powell stays back and flicks it to mid-wicket.
A length ball, on the pads. Powell comes across and looks to clip it away but misses and gets hit on the pads. Down leg.
A maiden over for Abbas. A length ball, on off. Powell defends it to cover.
On a length, around off. Brathwaite stays back and guides it towards gully. The man there misfields and the batters sneak a quick run.
Back of a length and just outside off. Powell plays inside the line and misses. The ball zips past the outside edge.
Tap and run! A length ball, on off. Powell defends it to cover and takes off for a quick single. There is hardly any movement for the new ball.
A length ball, around the hips. Brathwaite stays back and tucks it to square leg.
Back of a length and sliding down the leg side. Brathwaite looks to flick it away but misses.
BEATEN! Good delivery to end the over for Afridi. On a length and outside off. The ball is moving away from the right-hander. Brathwaite looks to defend it out but pulls his blade back in time.
A full-length ball, on the pads. Powell stays back and clears his front leg. He flicks it through square leg for a single.

FOUR! Powell is up to the task. Ali has been finding it difficult today to get the right line and length. A full-length ball, going down leg. Powell clips it through square leg and the ball races away to the boundary.
A length ball, on the pads. Powell flicks it to fine leg for a couple now.
Ali conitnues to attack the leg stump. Full and on leg. Powell nudges it through square leg for a single now.
On a length, in the channel of uncertainty. Kraigg Brathwaite leaves it alone for the keeper.
Some away movement this time. A full-length delivery, outside off. The ball nips away after landing. Kraigg Brathwaite has no stroke to offer.
Good-length ball, outside off. Powell leaves it alone for the keeper.
Outside off, Powell leaves it alone yet again.
A length ball, sliding down the leg side. Powell looks to flick it away but misses.
Full and on off. Powell defends it to cover off the outer half.
A full-length ball, on middle. Powell gets squared up and defends it to the left.of gully off the outer half.
On a length, outside off. Powell leaves it alone. The ball dies before it reaches the keeper.
serves this one up, around off and this one shapes away. Brathwaite doesn't offer a shot.
Length ball, on off stump, edged down to gully by Kraigg Brathwaite.
Full and straight. Kraigg Brathwaite pats it back to the bowler.
Fuller delivery, on off and driven to mid off.
Length ball, on off and keeping low. Kraigg Brathwaite defends it to cover-point.

Edged but short of second slip. Hasan Ali bowls a probing delivery, around off and the ball moves away just a bit. Kraigg Brathwaite looks to block it out but the ball takes the outside edge and falls comfortably short of second slip.
FOUR! Full and wide, driven through point for a glorious boundary by Kieran Powell.
Full, around off. Powell drives it to cover.
Length ball, just outside off. Kieran Powell watchfully leaves it through to the keeper.
An action replay of the previous delivery as Powell leaves another one outside off.
Pitched up, on middle. Powell defends it on the off side.
Back of a length, on off and angling away from the left-hander. Powell guides it to third man and picks up a single.
Hasan Ali induces the outside edge but it falls short of gully. Length ball, angled across on off. Powell looks to push at it but gets the outside edge, luckily for him it falls short of gully.
Back of a length, on middle. Powell punches it off the back foot towards mid on and takes off for a quick run.
Length ball, on off. Brathwaite blocks it out.
Fuller delivery, on middle and leg. Kraigg Brathwaite nudges it towards mid-wicket.
A touch fuller, outside off. Kraigg Brathwaite with a comfortable leave.

OUT! RUN OUT! Excellent from Shaheen Afridi and lazy work from Kieran Powell. Fuller delivery, outside off and driven nicely through covers. Afridi gives the chase and the batters come back for three. There is a shy at the keeper's end and it deflects off Rizwan's gloves to the stumps. They appeal and the third umpire is referred. Powell's bat is over the line but in the air, shows the replay. He will be distraught with himself because this is the last thing West Indies needed. Pakistan have a breakthrough now, a lucky one though.
Howout: run out (Shaheen Afridi / Mohammad Rizwan)

Commentary: Length ball, angled in on middle and leg. Brathwaite stays back and flicks it to square leg.
Length ball, on off. Blocked out.
Back of a length, on off. Brathwaite defends it off the back foot.
Length ball, around off and this one shapes back in late. Kraigg Brathwaite with a confident leave.
Full, on off and kept out by Kraigg Brathwaite.
Fullish delivery, outside off, finds the outside edge of a blocking Kraigg Brathwaite. The ball lands way in front of second slip.
Pitched up, outside off and moving away. Alzarri Joseph leaves it alone.
Length ball, on the pads. Joseph clips it away through square leg and comes back for the third run before the fielder cuts it off.
FOUR! Expansive cover drive from Kraigg Brathwaite. Full and wide, driven beautifully through cover for a boundary.
Back of a length, on middle and squares up Kraigg Brathwaite who looks to play at it with soft hands. The ball takes the outside edge and falls short again of the slip cordon.
On a good length, around middle. Brathwaite hops and tucks it behind square for a run.
Length ball, outside off. Joseph looks to drive but misses.
Good length and outside off. The ball moves away. Brathwaite looks to go after it but misses.
Full and on the pads. Brathwaite tucks it to mid-wicket.
A full-length ball, around off. Brathwaite defends it out solidly.
Full and on off. The ball nips in a bit. Brathwaite defends it out solidly.
A length ball, around off. Kraigg Brathwaite looks to defend it out. The ball takes the outside edge and falls short of Imran Butt at second slip.
On off, pushed to cover.
Good length ball, outside off. Joseph leaves it alone for the keeper.
A full-length ball, on off. Joseph defends it out watchfully.
On a length and outside off. Joseph lets it go to the keeper.
A length ball, on the pads. Joseph tucks it to mid-wicket.
On a length, in the channel of uncertainty. Joseph stays back and looks to play the off drive but misses. The ball beats the outside edge.
A length ball, on off. Joseph moves away and defends it out solidly.
Full and straight. Brathwaite defends it to short mid on.
LEG BYE! Fullish delivery, sliding down leg. Kraigg Brathwaite looks to flick but gets it off the pads towards fine leg. They get a leg bye.
Length, on top of off. Joseph defends it to cover-point.
Pitched up, on off. Alzarri Joseph stays solid in defense.
Short ball, on middle and leg. Alzarri Joseph takes his eye off the ball and tries to duck under it. The ball goes off the handle of the bat and lands well short of mid-wicket.
Length ball, outside off. Left alone by Alzarri Joseph.
Full and sliding down leg. Kraigg Brathwaite turns it to deep backward square leg for one.
FOUR! What timing from Alzarri Joseph! Length ball, on middle. Joseph hits it through mid-wicket and the ball races into the fence.
Pitched up, around off. Joseph with a stylish leave.
Fullish delivery, outside off. Alzarri Joseph with another leave. Mohammad Rizwan throws the ball back on the stumps, just to keep a check on the batter.
Length ball, angled in on middle and leg. Joseph looks to flick but misses and gets hit on the thigh pad.
A single to end the day. Pitched up, on off. Alzarri Joseph looks to drive but gets it off the inner half of the bat towards fine leg. That's the end of play on Day 4. Stumps!
FOUR! What a start from Alzarri Joseph! Pitched up on middle and punched past mid on for a lovely boundary.
Fullish delivery, pushed wider. Joseph leaves it alone.
Full and wide, close to the tramline. Joseph doesn't poke at it.
Right on the money and solidly blocked out by Joseph.

Huge mix-up! Joseph nudges the length ball on off towards mid-wicket and sets off for the single. Kraigg Brathwaite doesn't even look at him and Joseph is halfway down the pitch. The throw is at the bowler's end which gives Joseph time to scamper back. The last thing the hosts want here is another run out.
Length ball, outside off. Joseph shoulders arms to it.
Pitched up, on off. Kraigg Brathwaite blocks it out.
FOUR! Classical cover drive from Kraigg Brathwaite. Overpitched delivery, around off and Brathwaite just times it beautifully through covers and into the fence.
Back of a length, on off. Brathwaite tucks it off the back foot behind square on the leg side for a couple of runs.
Length again, on top of off. Blocked out by Brathwaite.
Abbas bowls a probing outswinger, around the fifth stump. Brathwaite looks to push at it but the ball whizzes past the outside edge.
Another outswinger, pitched up and outside off. Brathwaite leaves it alone.
Pitched up, wide outside off. Joseph leaves it with ease.
Full and wide. Left alone by Alzarri Joseph.
Pitched up, on middle and shaping in. Joseph works it to wide of mid on for a single.
Banged into the deck, around off. Brathwaite hops to defend.
Full, around off and pushed towards mid off.
Full again, on off. Kraigg Brathwaite pats it back to the bowler.
Pitched up, on off. Joseph stays solid in defense.
Length ball, on off. Joseph lifts it over mid off for a couple of runs.
On a length, around off. Joseph works it to mid-wicket.
Back of a length, outside off and this one bounces a bit extra. Alzarri Joseph shoulders arms.
Length, angled in on middle. Joseph keeps it out.
Pitched up, on middle and Joseph looks to drive on the up. He toe-ends it past mid on for a couple of runs.
Short of a length, outside off and angled away from the right-hander. Brathwaite with a good leave.
Length ball, on top of off. Brathwaite puts out a stride and defends it on the off side.
LEG BYE! Back of a length, on the hips. Brathwaite looks to flick but gets it off the thigh pad down to fine leg for a leg bye.
Short ball, banged in on middle stump. Alzarri Joseph does well to duck under it.

OUT! TAKEN! Alzarri Joseph has to depart and it's that man again, Shaheen Afridi, who provides the breakthrough. Afridi bowls a well-directed bouncer, around off stump. Joseph is forced to play at it and he can't get the pull under control. Joseph top-edges it behind the stumps and the keeper, Mohammad Rizwan, settles under it nicely and takes a simple catch.
Howout: c Mohammad Rizwan b Shaheen Afridi

Commentary: Length ball, angled away outside off. Bonner lets it through to the keeper.
Length ball, skidding in on middle and leg. Brathwaite nudges it to mid-wicket.
On a good length, outside off. This one bounces a bit extra and nips back in off the surface. Brathwaite looks to defend but the ball takes the glove and rolls on the leg side.
Length again, on off and nipping back in sharply. Brathwaite looks to block but gets caught on the crease and gets hit high on the pads.
BEAUTY! Abbas pitches this one up in that corridor of uncertainty and this time it shapes away. Brathwaite looks to push it out but the ball goes agonizingly past the outside edge.
Back of a length, on middle. Brathwaite rocks back and tucks it towards square leg for a run.
Pitched up and swinging back in from outside off. Bonner leaves it alone.
Fuller ball, on middle. Clipped to deep mid-wicket for one.
Short ball, angling away. Left alone.
Fuller ball, on leg. Bonner works it to deep square leg for a couple.
On a length, on leg. Bonner blocks it out.
Shorter ball, on off. Left alone.
Short again, on middle. Bonner ducks under it.
Short of a length, around off. Kraigg Brathwaite blocks it out.
Length ball, on leg. Worked to the leg side.
Length ball, down leg. Kraigg Brathwaite misses the flick.
Fuller ball, on leg. Clipped to mid-wicket.
Fuller ball, on off. Kraigg Brathwaite is solid in his defence of this one.
Back of a length, outside off. Kraigg Brathwaite gets behind the ball and blocks it out.

OUT! LBW! Three reds and Bonner is gone! Ali bowls a length ball, on off. It lands and comes back in. Bonner looks to block but gets hit on the pads. There is a huge appeal but turned down. Babar Azam decides to review this. There is no bat on that and Ball Tracker shows three reds! Great review by Pakistan! West Indies need 260 win and Roston Chase walks out to bat.
Howout: lbw b Hasan Ali

Commentary: Fuller ball, wide enough for Chase to leave it.
Back of a length, outside off. Left alone.
Outswinger but starts outside off. Left alone.
On a length, on leg. Blocked out.
Length ball, wide outside off. Chase covers the stumps and then leaves it alone.
Fuller ball, on leg. Blocked out.
Fuller on the pads. Kraigg Brathwaite works it past short leg.
Abbas is keeping it full and straight. For now, Kraigg Brathwaite is solid with his defence.
On a length, on off. Blocked out with ease.
Inswinger, lands on off and comes back in. Kraigg Brathwaite gets his bat down to defend it.
Fuller ball, on off. Kraigg Brathwaite leans into it and blocks it.
Length ball, down leg. Chase misses the flick.
Length ball, outside off. Left alone.
Back of a length, on off. Chase blocks it out.
Short of a length, outside off. Chase covers the stumps and then lets it go.
Ali bowls a length ball, on top of off. Chase stays in the crease and then blocks it.
Goog-length ball, on the fourth stump. Chase leaves it untouched.
Ashraf starts with a pitched up delivery, on off. Brathwaite defends it off the front foot.
Back of a length, around off. Brathwaite hops and blocks it out.

DROPPED! Abid Ali has dropped a sitter at first slip. On a good length around off and this one bounces a bit extra. Brathwaite is caught off guard with the extra bounce and the ball takes the gloves and pops up to first slip. Ali moves to his left but fails to hold on to it. Could this be the stroke of luck West Indies need?
FOUR! Adding insult to injury. A touch short and wide. Brathwaite hangs back and just guides it through the cover-point region and into the fence.
Fullish delivery, outside off. Brathwaite leaves it alone.
Full and wide again. Brathwaite isn't going to play at that.
Right on the money. Chase works it to short mid on.
Pitched up again, angled in on middle. Chase drives it on the up without any timing and the ball goes towards short mid on.
Fuller delivery, sliding in on the pads. Chase looks to flick but the ball hits the pads and rolls onto the leg side.

OUT! CAUGHT! Imran Butt has taken a blinder at second slip. Hasan Ali sets up Roston Chase nicely as he keeps on angling it in and then finally bowls the one that goes away. Pitched up, on off and Chase drives at it but with no feet movement. Chase ends up paying the ultimate price as the ball takes the outside edge and Imran Butt dives to his right to take a superb slip catch.
Howout: c Imran Butt b Hasan Ali

Commentary: Ali hits the length hard, on off. Blackwood defends it off the back foot.
Length ball, angled on the pads. Blackwood flicks it fine and gets a single down to fine leg.
Length ball, angled in on middle and leg. Blackwood manages to keep it out.
PLAY AND A MISS! Ashraf bowls this one fuller, outside off and the ball holds its line. Blackwood looks for the expansive drive but gets beaten on the outside edge.
Length ball, around off. Blackwood puts out a stride to block it.
FOUR! Overpitched and punished. Blackwood leans into the cover drive and crashes it through the infield into the boundary.
Length again, around off. Blackwood stays solid in defense.
Pitched up, on off. Blackwood defends it back to the bowler.
Length ball, on the pads. Brathwaite works it behind square on the leg side for a run.
Full and wide, Blackwood drives it through covers for a couple of runs.
Fullish delivery, on off. Blackwood nudges it to mid-wicket.
Length, outside off. Blackwood makes a leave and the ball dies on its way to the keeper.
Length again, on top of off. Blackwood blocks it out.
BEATEN! Ali bowls this one on a length around off and it shapes in nicely. Blackwood looks to defend but the ball goes between bat and pad through to the keeper.
On a length, around off. Barthwaite keeps it out.
Back of a length, on the hips. Brathwaite looks to tuck but gets hit on the pads.
Slightly pitched up on off. Brathwaite defends it solidly.
On a good length, outside off. Brathwaite makes a late but good leave.
Back of a length, outside off. This one keeps a bit low and Brathwaite hops to keep it out.
Length ball, outside off. Brathwaite leaves it alone. End of a maiden over from Faheem Ashraf.
Length ball, on off. Blocked out.
Back of a length, wide outside off. Left alone by Jermaine Blackwood.
On a length, on off. Jermaine Blackwood is solid in his defence.
A nice off drive but straight towards mid off.
Shorter ball, on off. Jermaine Blackwood sways away from it.
Length ball, on off. Jermaine Blackwood offers a solid defence off the front foot.
Shorter ball, around off. Pushed to covers.
Short ball, outside off. Kraigg Brathwaite chops it back to the keeper.
Full ball, way down the leg side. Mohammad Rizwan dives to his left to gather this one.
Shorter ball, outside off. Kraigg Brathwaite ducks under it.
Length ball, on off. Clipped to the leg side.
On a length, on off. Kraigg Brathwaite blocks it from the crease.
Shorter ball, on off. Pushed to covers.
Fuller ball, on off. Jermaine Blackwood stays in his crease and blocks it.
FOUR! Length ball, outside off. Jermaine Blackwood looks to block but gets the outside edge. The ball goes past gully and runs to the fence.
Full ball, down leg. Jermaine Blackwood misses the flick.
Back of a length, lands outside off and nips back in. Jermaine Blackwood looks to defend but gets hit high on the pads. A muted appeal and turned down.
On a length, outside off. Blocked out by Jermaine Blackwood.
Loopy ball, on off. Blocked out.
Flatter ball, on off. Pushed to covers.
Loopy ball, on off. Kraigg Brathwaite blocks it out.
Fuller ball, on off. Kraigg Brathwaite blocks it out.
Flatter ball, outside off. Pushed to covers.
Shorter ball, on off. Kraigg Brathwaite stays in the crease and blocks it.
Fuller ball, on off. Pushed to mid off and the midfield allows the single.
Tap and run. Length ball, on off. Kraigg Brathwaite taps it to mid on for a quick single. There is a direct hit at the bowler's end but Brathwaite is safe.
Back of a length, outside off. Pushed past covers for a single.
Length ball, on leg. Clipped past square leg for one.
Fuller ball, on off. Blocked out.
Back of a length, outside off. Blocked out.
Tossed up, outside off. Jermaine Blackwood blocks it.
Fuller ball, on middle. Pushed back to the bowler.
Quicker ball, around off. Jermaine Blackwood gets forward to block it.
Fuller ball, on off. Pushed past covers.
Tossed up, outside off. Blocked out. No ball called as Ali had overstepped.
Shorter ball, around off. Punched back to the bowler.
Darted on the pads. Swept to fine leg for one.
Length ball, on middle. Jermaine Blackwood works it to fine leg for one.
Fuller ball, on leg. Clipped to the leg side.
Back of a length, around off. Kraigg Brathwaite stays in the crease and blocks it.
Length ball, on leg. Brathwaite gets hit on the pads while looking to flick.
Fuller ball, on off. Blocked back to the bowler.
Back of a length, outside off. Kraigg Brathwaite gets forward and blocks it.
Tossed up, on off. Blocked out by Blackwood.
Loopy ball, full on middle. Blackwood caresses it to mid on.
FOUR! A touch shorter, outside off. Blackwood rocks back and cuts it to the vacant third man fence.
Angled in full and on middle. Blackwood defends it out.
Flatter one, sliding down leg. Blackwood nudges it behind square and picks up a couple.
Flighted, on off. Blackwood puts out a stride to defend it.
Full, inswinging delivery, on middle. Brathwaite looks to flick but the ball comes off the inside edge and onto the pads.
Afridi pitches this one up, outside off. Brathwaite hangs back and looks to drive but the ball beats the inside edge. There might have been an inside edge on it, but didn't carry to the keeper
Back of a length, on off. Brathwaite defends it off the back foot.
Length ball, around off. Blocked out by Brathwaite.
Back of a length, on middle stump. Brathwaite gets cramped for room as he blocks this one out.
Length ball, around off. Brathwaite taps it on the off side. End of a maiden over from Shaheen Afridi.
Tossed up, on off. Blackwood defends it out solidly.
An action replay of the previous delivery as Blackwood blocks this one out as well.
Loopy ball, on off. Kept out by Blackwood.
Tossed up again, on middle. Blackwood defends it off the front foot.
Flatter one, sliding in on leg stump. Blackwood works it towards deep square leg for one.
Flighted, on off. Brathwaite stays solid in defense.
Pitched up, around off and driven nicely to cover by Blackwood.
Fullish ball, outside off. Blackwood hops and lets it through to the keeper.
Afridi angles this one on middle from around the wicket. Jermaine Blackwood tucks it to mid-wicket.
Full and sliding down leg. Blackwood flicks it to fine leg for a run.
Full and on middle. Brathwaite manages to defend it on the leg side.
Back of a length, sliding way down the leg side. Kraigg Brathwaite doesn't play at it and it's a good take from Mohammad Rizwan diving down to his left.
A touch shorter, outside off and this one turns away sharply. Blackwood watchfully lets it go.
Tossed up, outside off. Blackwood puts out a stride and leaves it alone.

OUT! CAUGHT BEHIND! Nauman Ali has done the trick just before Lunch. He tosses this one up, around off and this one grips and bounces a bit extra as well. Jermaine Blackwood looks to block it out by the delivery is just too good. The ball takes the outside edge of Blackwood's bat and Mohammad Rizwan takes a sharp catch behind the stumps.
Howout: c Mohammad Rizwan b Nauman Ali

Commentary: Loopy ball, angled in on middle. Mayers manages to block it out.
Tossed up, on middle. Awkwardly defended by Mayers.
Shorter delivery, around off. Mayers rocks back and punches it towards cover.
Length ball, on off and just holds into the surface a bit. Brathwaite watchfully keeps it out.
Full and angled in on middle. Brathwaite drives it to mid on.
Length ball, outside off. Brathwaite doesn't play at it. This one dies on its way to the keeper.
WIDE! Bangs in a short one, around off. Brathwaite manages to duck under it. A bit too high and a wide is called.
FOUR! Overpitched and punished. Kraigg Brathwaite keeps his balance as he drives this one beautifully through covers for a boundary.
Back of a length, around off. Brathwaite taps it on the leg side.
Full and sliding way down leg. Brathwaite leaves it alone and another good take by Mohammad Rizwan down to his left.
Shorter one, on middle. Mayers rocks back and works it to dep mid-wicket for a run. He gets off the mark for the first time in this series!
Arm ball, outside off and left alone.
Flatter one, on off. Brathwaite blocks it out.
Flatter and quicker, outside off. Brathwaite leaves it alone.
Tossed up, on middle. Brathwaite defends it back to the bowler.
Another one grips and turns. Flighted, around off and beats Brathwaite all ends up as he looks to defend.
Pitched up, on off. Mayers punches it to short cover.
On a length, outside off. Mayers isn't going to offer a stroke.
EDGED and SAFE! Full and wide from Afridi, inviting the drive. Kyle Mayers goes for the expansive drive and gets a thick edge through backward point. They take two.
Pitched up, on off. Blocked out by Mayers.
Length ball, angled in on the pads. Mayers looks to flick but gets it off the thigh pad and Rizwan dives down to his right to make a good stop.
Length ball, on off. Mayers stays solid in defense.
Full and quick, outside off. Brathwaite hops back to block it out.
Flighted ball, around off. Brathwaite puts out a stride and blocks it out.
A touch shorter, around off. Brathwaite works it off the back foot to point.
FOUR! Short and wide, Kraigg Brathwaite takes full advantage of it. He rocks back and cuts it behind point for a boundary.
Tossed up, on off. Brathwaite drives it to mid off.
Brathwaite successfully negotiates the final delivery before Lunch. Ali gives it air and bowls it slower, around off. Brathwaite watchfully keeps it out. Lunch is called on Day 5.
Ali starts with a length ball, outside off. Mayers leaves this alone.
Another length ball, outside off. Tempting Mayers to drive but the southpaw leaves it again.
Fuller ball, on off. Pushed back to the bowler. Ali throws it at the stumps but misses.
On a length, just outside off. Mayers covers his stumps and then lets it go.
Good-length ball, outside off. Mayers looks to defend but the ball goes past the outside edge.
Short of a length, outside off. Left alone.
Flatter ball, outside off. Pushed to covers.
Loopy ball, on off. Blocked out.

OUT! TAKEN! Nauman Ali gets the big fish! This is a poor shot by Kraigg Brathwaite. This is short and wide outside off. Kraigg Brathwaite goes for the cut but hits it in the air. Fawad Alam at point takes the simplest of catches and sends back the West Indies skipper!
Howout: c Fawad Alam b Nauman Ali

Commentary: Loopy ball, on off. Blocked out.
SIX! All the way! Tossed up, on off. Holder smokes it over the long off fence.
Tossed up, on off. Holder looks to drive but gets the inside edge on the leg side.
Fuller ball, outside off. Left alone.
Short ball, on leg. Mayers pulls it to deep square leg for a single.
On a length, on off. Holder stays in his crease to block it.
Fuller ball, on off. Holder blocks it under his eyes.
Length ball, wide enough for Holder to leave it alone.
Full ball, outside off. Holder looks to leave it late and the ball hits the bat and goes towards slips.
Flatter ball, on off. Mayers blocks it out.
Loopy ball, on off. Mayers defends it with his bat and pad close together.
Shorter ball, outside off. Mayers cuts it past covers for two. The throw comes in from deep and Rizwan takes the bails off but Mayers is well in.
Loopy ball, on off. Blocked out.
Sharp turn! Flatter ball, on off. This comes back in sharply. Mayers goes back and blocks it out.
Fuller ball, on leg. Pushed to the leg side.
Length ball, on top of off. Holder blocks it out.
Full and wide. Holder dabs it towards the cover-point region and Fawad Alam runs around to keep it to a single.
FOUR! Classy shot from Kyle Mayers. Length ball, outside off. Mayers just guides it through backward point and into the fence.
Full, on middle. Mayers works it through mid-wicket for a couple of runs.
Banged in short, on middle. Mayers looks to pull but the ball hurries onto him. He misses the shot and gets hit on the arm.
Pitched up, around off. Left alone.
Looped up, on off. Holder taps it to silly point.
Nicely flighted, on off. Holder drives it to short cover.
Fuller one, on middle. Blocked out.
A slider, on middle and leg. Holder stays solid in defense.
Ali flights this one up, outside off and gets the turn. Holder looks to cover drive but gets beaten by the spin.
Tossed up, outside off. Holder leaves it alone and it's a maiden over from Nauman Ali.
Very full, from around the wicket and on off. Mayers manages to keep it out.
Length ball, around off. Left alone.
No Ball! A quick bumper, angled in on middle and leg. Mayers ducks under it. A no ball is called for overstepping.
Pitched up, around off. Beats the outside edge of Mayers.
FOUR! Pitched up again, around off. Mayers opens the face of the bat and drives it past gully for a boundary.
Fuller one, on middle. Kept out by Mayers.
Length, outside off and left alone.
Flighted delivery, on off. Holder defends on the off side.
Tossed up, around off. Holder drives it straight to silly point, who gets hit on the shin.
Loopy ball, around off again. Holder watchfully keeps it out.
Tossed up, fuller and outside off. Holder drives it through covers and comes back for the second.
Flatter one, on off and kept out by Holder.
Nicely floated, outside off. Holder doesn't make a play at it.
FOUR! Pure timing from Kyle Mayers who is beaming with confidence now. Pitched up, on middle and Mayers drives it past the bowler and into the fence.
FOUR! Short of a length, on middle and muscled away by Mayers. Mayers pulls it through mid-wicket for another boundary.
No Ball! Length ball, around off and caressed towards point. No ball called for overstepping.
Length ball, on off. Blocked out.
Length ball, outside off and left alone.
A touch short and wide. Mayers thrashes it but straight to point.
Fullish delivery, on off. Mayers squeezes it to the cover-point region.
Loopy ball, on off. Pushed to covers.
Tossed up, around off. Holder looks to block but the ball zips past the outside edge.
Just a single as Holder pushes this towards long off.
Full ball, on the pads. Whipped to deep mid-wicket for one. No ball called for overstepping.
Tossed up, outside off. Left alone.
Fuller ball, on off. Holder prods forward and blocks it.
Darted on the pads. Tucked to the leg side for one.
Back of a length, on off. Holder looks to defend but gets the inside edge back on the pads.
Length ball, outside off. Holder looks to push it away but gets beaten.
Fuller ball, on leg. Holder works it towards mid-wicket.
On a length, outside off. Holder stays in the crease and then blocks it out.
Length ball, on off. Blocked out.

Just short! Length ball, around off. Holder gets the outside edge while looking to defend. But the ball lands just short of second slip. The fielder gets a hand to it but the ball rolls away. The other fielder chases the ball and dives to stop it before the ropes. Two taken.
Tossed up, on off. Pushed to mid-wicket.
Flighted ball, outside off. Pushed back to the bowler.
Fuller and quicker now, in the line of the stumps. Mayers blocks it out.
Quicker ball, on leg. Tucked to mid-wicket.
Shorter ball, on leg. Pushed to mid-wicket.

DROPPED! Flatter ball, on off. Mayers gets the inside edge back on the pads. The ball goes to the right of short leg. Abid Ali dives and gets his hands to it but the ball pops out. Ali is not at all impressed.
Back of a length, on off. Blocked out.
Fuller ball, on off. Pushed to covers. No ball called for overstepping.
Back of a length, around off. Holder blocks it out.
Shorter ball, outside off. Holder pushes it to covers.
On a length, on the off pole. Holder looks to work it away but gets hit high on the pads.
Full ball, but wide enough for Holder to leave it.
Full again, but this is closer to the off pole. Holder gets forward and blocks it.
Flatter ball, outside off. Mayers pushes it past cover for one.
Flatter ball, on off. Blocked out.
Shorter ball, on off. Holder pushes it to covers.
Tossed up, on leg. Holder pushes it back to the bowler.
Shorter ball, outside off. Holder cuts it but the man at short cover dives and stops the ball.
Loopy ball, on off. Drilled straight to short cover.
Full, sliding in on middle. Mayers flicks it to deep square and picks up a couple of runs.
FOUR! Deliberate from Kyle Mayers. Length ball, around off and Mayers guides it through the slip cordon and into the fence.

OUT! CAUGHT BEHIND! Kyle Mayers has thrown it away and he'll be disappointed with himself. Pitched up, on off and swinging away. Mayers looks to drive across the line and gets the outside edge. Mohammad Rizwan dives to his left and takes a nice catch. Shaheen Afridi has been consistently providing the visitors with crucial breakthroughs and he does not disappoint when his skipper brought him on to do it again.
Howout: c Mohammad Rizwan b Shaheen Afridi

Commentary: A length ball, around off. Da Silva defends it to covers.
Full, outside off. Da Silva taps it back to the bowler who throws it back at the stumps.
Pitched up, on off. Joshua Da Silva stays solid in defense.
Flatter one, sliding down leg. Holder leaves it alone.
BEATEN! Flights this one up nicely, around off and this one grips and turns. Holder looks to block but gets beaten.
Nicely flighted again and again beats the outside edge of Jason Holder. Around off and turns away, Holder looks to block but gets beaten.
Full, on the stumps. Holder nudges it on the off side for a run.
A touch shorter on middle. Joshua Da Silva gets off the mark with a single down to deep mid-wicket.
This one is pushed slower through the air and bowled around off. Holder blocks it out.
Pitched up, on off. Joshua Da Silva gets it off the inner half towards mid on.
PLAY AND A MISS! Length ball, outside off. Da Silva looks to drive but gets beaten by the pace of the delivery.
A quick bumper, angled in on leg stump. Da Silva manages to duck under it.
Length ball, sliding down leg. Glanced off the hip towards fine leg for a single.
Pitched up, on middle. Holder blocks it out solidly.
CLOSE! Full, around off and Holder looks to cover drive. He gets it off the inside edge and past the leg stump towards fine leg for a single.
Tossed up, on off. Holder defends it well.
Slower one, on leg stump. Holder waits for it and works it through mid-wicket for a couple of runs.
Flatter one, on off. Holder blocks it out.
Uppish but safe. Floated, on off. Holder drives it on the bounce to cover.
Flighted ball, on middle. Holder turns it to the leg side.
Tossed up, around off and blocked out by Holder.
Length ball, angling across to the right-hander and pushed wider. Joshua Da Silva leaves it alone.
Length again, on top of off. Da Silva defends it off the back foot.
Pitched up, on off, from around the wicket. Joshua Da Silva drives it to mid off where the fielder fumblea a bit. No run taken though.
Fullish delivery, on off. Da Silva flicks it to mid-wicket.
This one is pitched up on off. Da Silva stays solid in defense.
FOUR! Sweetly timed by Joshua Da Silva. Full and straight and driven past mid on for a boundary. That will make Joshua Da Silva feel much better.
FOUR! Shorter ball, on off. Holder pulls it past mid on for a boundary.
SIX! Just over the fielder! Tossed up, on off. Holder lofts it to long off. Shaheen Afridi leaps up and gets a hand to it but the momentum takes him over the ropes.
Loopy ball, on off. Driven to covers.
Tossed up, on off. Blocked out.
Just a single as Holder pushes it to long off.
Tossed up, on off. Joshua Da Silva blocks it out.
FOUR! Top shot. Full ball, on leg. Holder whips it past mid on for a boundary.
On a length, around off. Blocked out.
Full ball, outside off. Holder leans forward and pushes it to mid off.
Shorter ball, outside off. Holder pushes it past covers for a couple.
A touch fuller, on off. Holder blocks it out.
Length ball, around off. Holder strides forward and blocks it out.
Fuller ball, on off. Pushed back to the bowler.
Tossed up, way outside off. Left alone.
Loopy ball, on off. Joshua Da Silva pushes it back to the bowler.
Nicely tossed up, on middle. A nice stride is put in by Joshua Da Silva to defend this.
Fuller ball, outside off. Left alone.
Flatter ball, outside off. Da Silva pushes it to covers.
Full ball, on off. Holder leans forward and blocks it.
Fuller ball, on off. Holder nudges it to mid on.
FOUR! Nicely done. On a length, outside off. Holder runs it past the slip cordon and gets a boundary.
Good-length ball, on the fourth stump. Holder pushes it to cover.
Full ball, outside off. Holder leans into it and plays it to cover.
Length ball, on off. Holder runs it past point for one.
Tossed up, on off. Blocked out.
Loopy ball, around off. Holder clips it to mid on.
Nicely tossed up, outside off. Pushed to covers.
Fuller ball, on off. Holder comes forward to block it.
FOUR! Smacked! Tossed up, outside off. Jason Holder frees his arms and thrashes it past covers for a boundary.
Loopy ball, on off. Blocked out.
Darted in, on off. Kept out by Da Silva.
Quicker one, sliding down leg. Joshua Da Silva looks to flick and gets hit on the pads.
Fuller one, on middle. Turned to mid-wicket.
Shorter delivery, on middle and leg. Da Silva tucks it to mid-wicket.
A touch shorter, on middle and kept out by Joshua Da Silva.
Short again, on middle. Da Silva keeps it out. Maiden over from Fawad Alam.
FOUR! Tossed up, outside off and once again Jason Holder drives it through covers for a boundary.

OUT! CAUGHT! One drive too many from Jason Holder and this might just be the final nail in the coffin for West Indies. This one is flighted nicely, around off. Jason Holder plays an uppish drive and holds out to cover. Fawad Alam gets low and pouches an important catch. Nauman Ali has been rewarded for his continued probing.
Howout: c Fawad Alam b Nauman Ali

Commentary: FOUR BYES! Tossed up, around off and this one beats everyone and races into the third man fence. 200 is up for West Indies.
Full, on middle. Roach defends it out.
Flighted nicely, on off and turning away just a bit. Roach looks to block but the ball goes past the outside edge.
Tossed up, on off and Roach blocks it out.
Flatter one, on middle and played towards mid on.
Full and quick, outside off. Da Silva drives it to cover.
Darted in on middle, Da Silva drives it to wide of mid on and takes a quick single.
Flatter one, angled in on middle. Roach manages to block it out.
Slower one, flighted on off. Kemar Roach watchfully keeps it out.
Flatter one, on the stumps. Kept out.
Loopy ball, just outside off. Joshua Da Silva makes a good leave.
Tossed up, full and on off. Da Silva drives it nicely to mid off.
Flighted, on off. Joshua Da Silva pats it back to the bowler.
This one is pushed wider and Joshua Da Silva leaves it alone.
Floated up, around off. Da Silva stays solid in defense.
Another dot to end. This one is flighted on middle and Da Silva keeps it out. Maiden over from Nauman Ali.
Full and quick, on off. Kept out by Roach.
Flatter one, on the pads. Roach sweeps it to deep square leg for one.
Full again, on off. Da Silva solidly defends it out.
Tossed up, on off and driven to mid off.
Tossed up, on off. Kept out by Da Silva.
Full, on middle. Joshua Da Silva pushes it to mid on and sets off for a quick single. The fielder fumbles allowing an easy run.
Flatter ball, outside off. Left alone.
Fuller ball, on off. Pushed to covers.
Flatter ball, on off. Joshua Da Silva blocks it out.
Shorter ball, on off. Pushed to mid on.
Shorter ball, on off. Pushed to mid off now.
Tossed up, on off. Pushed back to Ali by Da Silva.
Length ball, outside off. Left alone by Roach.
Very full and wide outside off. Roach carves it past point for a couple.
Length ball, down leg. Roach misses the flick.
Back of a length, on leg. Roach gets hit on the pads while looking to flick.
FOUR! Lovely shot. Full ball, on leg. Roach drives it down the ground for a boundary.

OUT! LBW! Shaheen Afridi strikes again! Length ball, lands on middle and nips back in. Roach is struck on the pads while looking to block it. The appeal is put in and the umpire's finger goes up. Roach decides to review this. No bat on that one and three reds on Ball Tracker! Just the one wicket remaining now for West Indies.
Howout: lbw b Shaheen Afridi

Commentary: Length ball, on leg. Worked to the leg side.
Fuller ball, outside off. Joshua Da Silva drives it past covers for one.
Length ball, on leg. Blocked out.
On a length, outside off. Joshua Da Silva pushes it past point for a quick single.
Length ball, on off. Blocked out.
Length ball, on leg. Seales gets hit on the pads as he looks to flick.
FOUR! Up and over! Full ball, on off. Da Silva lifts it over mid off for a boundary.

OUT! CAUGHT! That's it, Pakistan have leveled the series! Shaheen Afridi pitches this one up, on middle and Joshua Da Silva looks to take him on. Da Silva looks to go over mid on but only manages to find the fielder there, Faheem Ashraf who takes a simple catch. It is only fitting that Shaheen Afridi is the man to pick up the final wicket. PAKISTAN WIN BY 109 RUNS!
Howout: c Faheem Ashraf b Shaheen Afridi
